          <span class="bold">	Seconded active-duty military and police personnel</span>
        </docTitle>
      </p>
    </preface>
    <preamble>
      <formula name="enactingFormula" eId="formula_1">
        <p xml:space="preserve">
          <span class="italic">The General Assembly</span>,</p>
      </formula>
      <container name="Recalling" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recalling</span> its resolutions <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/67/287">67/287</a> of 28 June 2013, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/68/252">68/252</a> of 27 December 2013, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/71/263">71/263</a> of 23 December 2016, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/74/254">74/254</a> A of 27 December 2019, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/74/254B">74/254</a> B of 6 August 2020 and <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/75/292">75/292</a> of 30 June 2021 as well as its decision <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/78/542C">78/542</a> C of 24 April 2024,</p>
      </container>
      <container name="Having considered" eId="container_3">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Having considered</span> the report of the Secretary-General on seconded active-duty military and police personnel<authorialNote marker="1" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_1"><p xml:space="preserve">	 	<a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/78/602">A/78/602</a>.</p></authorialNote> and the related report of the Advisory Committee on Administrative and Budgetary Questions,<authorialNote marker="2" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_2"><p xml:space="preserve">	 	<a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/78/762">A/78/762</a>.</p></authorialNote> </p>
      </container>
